oboto, sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box;\" /&gt;&lt;span style=\"forced-color-adjust:none;color:#8094ae;font-family:Roboto, sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif;font-size:14px;\"&gt;{site_name}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 1, 'ar', 14),
